OL,3,CUK not ready to fight an all-out war
OL,4,Cdue to 'overstretched' army, MPs warn
OL,6,FBritain will not be ready to fight an
OL,7,Fall-out war unless the government
OL,8,Faddresses the lack of training and
OL,9,Frecruitment crisis faced by the army,
OL,10,FMPs have warned,
OL,12,FThe military is "consistently
OL,13,Foverstretched", with the demands of
OL,14,Foperations personnel leaving little
OL,15,Ftime for training in warfighting, the
OL,16,FCommons Defence Committee said.
OL,18,FMP's warning comes as the Defence
OL,19,Fcommittee report is due to be
OL,20,Fpublished.
