OL,3,CUK not ready to fight an all-out war
OL,4,Cdue to 'overstretched' army, MPs warn
OL,6,F"The government risks being unable to
OL,7,Fbuild true warfighting and strategic
OL,8,Freadiness because of the sheer pace of
OL,9,Foperations, which could threaten the
OL,10,Fsecurity of the UK," the report said.
OL,12,FThe panel suggested the "unrelenting
OL,13,Fpressure" on personnel has worsened
OL,14,Fthe army recruitment crisis and
OL,15,Fretention of both regulars and
OL,16,Freservists, with more people leaving
OL,17,Fthe Armed Forces than joining.
