OL,3,CUK not ready to fight an all-out war
OL,4,Cdue to 'overstretched' army, MPs warn
OL,6,FSir Jeremy Quin, who recently took
OL,7,Fover as Defence Committee chairman,
OL,8,Fsaid: "The military is unable to
OL,9,Fdevote sufficient training and
OL,10,Fresources to high-intensity
OL,11,Fwarfighting.
OL,13,F"Our inquiry found that readiness for
OL,14,Fall-out, prolonged war has received
OL,15,Finsufficient attention and needs
OL,16,Fintense ongoing focus.
