OL,3,CUK not ready to fight an all-out war
OL,4,Cdue to 'overstretched' army, MPs warn
OL,6,FThe committee's inquiry heard the
OL,7,Freduction in size of the Armed Forces
OL,8,Fsince 2010 means they would exhaust
OL,9,Ftheir capabilities "after the first
OL,10,Fcouple of months of" a peer-on-peer
OL,11,Fwar.
OL,13,FIt comes after Defence Secretary Grant
OL,14,FShapps last month said the world is
OL,15,F"moving from a post-war to pre-war
OL,16,Fworld" and the UK must ensure its
OL,17,F"entire defence ecosystem is ready" to
OL,18,Fdefend its homeland.
