OL,4,Cdue to 'overstretched' army, MPs warn
OL,6,FHe insisted the size of the Army will
OL,7,Fnot dip below 73,000 under the
OL,8,FConservatives, amid growing concerns
OL,9,Fabout further cuts to troop numbers.
OL,11,FThe committee also complained that its
OL,12,Finquiry was "hampered" by a "lack of
OL,13,Fgovernment transparency" and the
OL,14,F"unacceptably slow" response to its
OL,15,Frequests for information.
OL,17,FThe MoD has been contacted for comment.
